V5 never looked so good 

@ethixltd presenting the new 
Mr Steele V5 Motors. 
2307 1750KV SILK (White/pts Pink)
2307 1950KV STOUT (Mag Blue) 🥵 
After all the changes in camera platforms and performance characteristics the taller stator was a must have. There’s now more power where you want it and more torque where you need it. From professional applications to flying with friends the V5 offers new and improved bell design changes that feature even more durability. Check out the limited edition pts pink on the V5 SILKs 🥰

Thank you to all that have stood by me all of these years. I wouldn’t be here without your support.
